name: Osyotr
description:
This is my self-made silhouette of my soul, this will be the logo of my FINAL musical project, 
with which I will return to music until the end, whenever the end is.
I drew a reflection of the goal to which I went through EVERYTHING.
This is more than a foto of who I become and who I really always been.
This is me.
The inevitable result of all events in the universe.
The purpose of my life, from which I ran away, is to remind the world what music is.
And how important it is.
From now on, this world has me - Osyotr.
